                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t17871024-31-victim336 t17871024-31-viclabel174"></join>; I lost some wearing apparel the 27th of last month; I saw the prisoner once; I never saw her but once, that was at the office after she was taken; I lost this out of <placeName id="t17871024-31-crimeloc175">Kingsland-road</placeName>
